ActCanadian Forces Members and Veterans Re-establishment and Compensation Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Canadian Forces Members and Veterans Re-establishment and Compensation Regulations
PrecisRegulations amending the CANADIAN FORCES MEMBERS AND VETERANS RE-ESTABLISHMENT AND COMPENSATION REGULATIONS in order to enhance service delivery to participants of the Rehabilitation Program and fulfill the program intent of covering the eligible expenses directly associated with their training when it is required.
